o 3-month-olds include cradle and tummy to tummy, with two videos for variations on each position. For babies 3 to 6 months old, Zolowear recommends the kangaroo position, and for 6 months and up, it suggests the hip position. For toddlers 15 months and older, the hip or back method is ideal.","The Zolowear sling is available in three sizes, from small to large. Sizing is based on your build, not the baby&#39;s weight, so it&#39;s possible that Mom and Dad will each need a different size of baby sling. Proper sizing is vital to your baby&#39;s safety, so make sure you consult the size chart. Wearing the wrong size of sling can also be inconvenient for you; the zippered pocket may wind up in a poor position, or the sling could cause back pain.","These slings are made out of numerous materials, including cotton, mesh, organic cotton and silk. The type of material determines the washing instructions for the sling, but you should always hang these products to dry, and some slings may require ironing before using after washing."]},"id":"3b63a38a-95ea-48d3-9b1a-2afb1239f778","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_58776","url":"/zolowear-pleated-cotton-sling-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"grant-morgan","url":"/author/grant-morgan","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Grant Morgan","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"5h9THR5HH34dskUikqZYj8","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-02-03T23:52:06Z","datePublished":"2014-02-03T23:52:06Z","name":"Zolowear Pleated Cotton Sling","synopsis":"There are more ring-style baby slings than just the best-known brands. Zolowear offers everything you could want in a sling, in a variety of stylish patterns.","review":{"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"There are more ring-style baby slings than just the best-known brands. Zolowear offers everything you could want in a sling, in a variety of stylish patterns.","language":"en","d